There are 3 lifecycle events that take place in order:
    1. pre-download
    2. download
    3. post-download

Application provides hooks for each of these events when they are emitted.
    PRE_DOWNLOAD    ->      @PreDownloadPlugin
    DOWNLOAD        ->      @Download
    POST_DOWNLOAD   ->      @PostDownloadPlugin

* Must have auto update feature -> if a new video in the playlist is added/updated, it should automatically be downloaded and user should be reminded of the same